cs5700.hw1.myClasses.personClasses

Class MatchedPairCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs5700.hw1.myClasses.personClasses.MatchedPairCollection

  • public class MatchedPairCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    MatchedPairCollection contains an array list of matched pair objects. Methods include addToList() which creates a matchedPair object and stores it in the pairList array, and getSize() and getList() which return the size of the pairList and the pairList respectively.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Steven Proctor
